e cats attacks will apply a 2s slow to the enemy.u000au000aIf Guardians of Bast is active, she will command her guardians to also charge forward.","menuitems":[{"description":"Ability:","value":"Line"},{"description":"Affects:","value":"Enemy"},{"description":"Damage:","value":"Physical"}],"rankitems":[{"description":"Root Damage:","value":"60/95/130/165/200 (65% of your Physical Power)"},{"description":"Cat Damage:","value":"20/25/30/35/40 (0% of your Inhand Power)"},{"description":"Cat Hit Points:","value":"2"},{"description":"Lane Minion Damage:","value":"1 HP lost per 5 hits"},{"description":"Slow:","value":"25%"}]}},"abilityDescription4":{"itemDescription":{"cooldown":"90s","cost":"80/85/90/95/100","description":"Bastet calls her loyal Guardian cats to her side. These Guardians will follow Bastet's order, assisting her in any ability she casts and dealing a percentage of Bastet's damage.","menuitems":[{"description":"Ability:","value":"Stim"},{"description":"Affects:","value":"Self"},{"description":"Damage:","value":"Physical"}],"rankitems":[{"description":"Guardian Damage:","value":"20/25/30/35/40%"},{"description":"Duration:","value":"12s"}]}},"abilityDescription5":{"itemDescription":{"cooldown":"","cost":"","description":"When Bastet hits an enemy she marks the target for a brief time. Marked targets leave behind a scent trail Bastet can follow, gaining Movement Speed while in the scent trail.","menuitems":[{"description":"Ability:","value":"Debuff"},{"description":"Affects:","value":"Enemy"}],"rankitems":[{"description":"Scent Duration:","value":"3s"},{"description":"Movement Speed:","value":"20%"}]}},"basicAttack":{"itemDescription":{"cooldown":"","cost":"","description":"","menuitems":[{"description":"Damage:","value":"37 + 2.21/Lvl (+100% of Physical Power)"},{"description":"Progression:","value":"1/.7/1.3x damage"}],"rankitems":[]}},"godAbility1_URL":"https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/pounce.jpg","godAbility2_URL":"https://web2.hirez.com/smite/